name: Tubee
overview: Tubee is a mobile application that changes watching television into a social, interactive, and augmented experience. The application allows users to check into a TV show they are watching and chat in real time with those in their neighbourhood, town or city watching the show with them. Users can check-in to the show they are watching on facebook, chat with those in their area, or tweet any comment they find entertaining. Users are able to view and add show reviews and ratings, view show information and additional images and videos. Tubee connects fans of shows, augments the television watching experience and allows users to discover new shows and new friends.
